      "title": "模型框架适配与部署基线技能",
      "description": "基于 PyTorch 框架的昇腾 NPU 模型推理适配与部署基线技能。从 HF 链接或本地模型代码出发，按 cann-recipes-infer",
      "category": "external",
      "source": "cannbot",
      "path": "external/cannbot/model/model-infer-migrator",
