      "originalName": "triton-operator-performance-optim",
      "title": "Triton 算子性能优化（Ascend NPU）",
      "description": "优化 Ascend NPU 亲和的 Triton 算子性能。解决 UB 溢出、提高 Cube 利用率、Tiling 策略设计。关键词：性能优化、performance",
      "category": "external",
      "source": "gitcode-ascend",
      "path": "external/gitcode-ascend/triton-operator-performance-optim",
      "skillFile": "external/gitcode-ascend/triton-operator-performance-optim/SKILL.md",
      "githubUrl": "https://github.com/ascend-ai-coding/awesome-ascend-skills/blob/main/external/gitcode-ascend/triton-operator-performance-optim/SKILL.md",
